Merge pull request #20 from AnandkumarSP/master

Changed to Float64Array

Changed to Float64Array

Float32Arrays do not represent numbers as accurately (Ref:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/8542414/javascript-float32array-wierdness).
It results in noticable difference when converting the FFT output to dB
scale.
